elvetica;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"><img alt="07170203.jpg" width="640" height="422" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170802/1501662996916576.jpg"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;color: rgb(116, 116, 116);font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, SimSun, Arial, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;color: rgb(116, 116, 116);font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, SimSun, Arial, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0px;color: rgb(116, 116, 116);font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, SimSun, Arial, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(237, 125, 49)"><span style="font-family:宋体">培养所向无敌的能力是职场的核心竞争力法则。</span></span></strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent"></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transp